COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10a
STRING: [Phorni] “Alright, get up and get ready for school. It's
already after nine o'clock.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13e
STRING: I felt like I'd been sleeping lightly since the day before.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14a
STRING: I felt like I kept having the same dream, but I had
already forgotten it, and I couldn't remember anything.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16a
STRING: Even so, I went to sleep right after Torta left, so I didn't
feel a lack of sleep.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x180
STRING: [Chris] “Phorni...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b2
STRING: [Phorni] “Morning. You have school from today;
shouldn't you get ready soon?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d2
STRING: She hadn't shown herself for two days, and that's what
she said the moment she appeared...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1e8
STRING: [Chris] “I've been calling you for the past two days; why
didn't you come out?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x224
STRING: [Phorni] “Obviously because I wanted time to think
alone? I'll come out any time if it's necessary, but I didn't
think it was.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x24e
STRING: [Chris] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x280
STRING: [Phorni] “I mean, Chris, you have Asino and Torta...
Friends that will worry about you.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2a0
STRING: [Chris] “There are things I can't talk to either of them
about.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2d2
STRING: [Phorni] “Then it's better you don't talk to me. You need
to face reality more, Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2f2
STRING: [Chris] “What's wrong with you today...? Saying that all
of the sudden.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x312
STRING: It wasn't Phorni's normal tone.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x31e
STRING: Even though I knew what she was saying was right, I
just couldn't accept it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x350
STRING: [Phorni] “I'm worried about you Chris... Everyone is. So
when you really need it, it's okay to depend on them.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x37a
STRING: [Chris] “Ha-ha-ha... I can't believe I'm hearing this from
you, Phorni.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3ac
STRING: [Phorni] “If you can chat like this, it's enough. Come on,
you don't have much time.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3cc
STRING: [Chris] “Is it that time already?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3fe
STRING: [Phorni] “Weren't you listening? You have less than
twenty minutes. Get ready quick, and get going.
Practice hard.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x41e
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah I know...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x448
STRING: I knew that Phorni was showing me she cared with this
innocuous interaction.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x45e
STRING: There were many people supporting me, and I was a
problem for them.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x46a
STRING: With gratitude and guilt in my heart, I said goodbye to
Phorni and went outside.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4f4
STRING: [Torta] “Oh, morning.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x50a
STRING: Torta must have been waiting for me, as she called out
to me from the entrance to the school.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x520
STRING: [Chris] “Morning.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x536
STRING: I answered her and we entered the school together.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x55c
STRING: I looked into the windows of the row of practice rooms
as I walked down the hallway.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x568
STRING: Half of them were filled with faces I recognized,
probably third year students.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x57e
STRING: [Chris] “It's pretty crowded...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5b0
STRING: [Torta] “Of course. But it's okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5c6
STRING: [Chris] “Hmm?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5e4
STRING: [Torta] “I came early and put my bag down.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5fa
STRING: Saying this, she headed for the door of the practice
room in front of us.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x606
STRING: [Chris] “Your bag? You're well prepared.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x638
STRING: [Torta] “That's because I have to cover for Mr.
Unprepared.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x658
STRING: [Chris] “You're absolutely right.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x68a
STRING: [Torta] “You're supposed to deny it...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6a0
STRING: [Chris] “No, I can't.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6d2
STRING: [Torta] “＊sigh＊ Whatever.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6e8
STRING: Torta sighed as if unimpressed, and opened the door of
the practice room.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x730
STRING: [Chris] “That's a little unsafe.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x746
STRING: Her bag was just sitting on a chair.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x76e
STRING: [Torta] “But most people go away as soon as they see
it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x784
STRING: [Chris] “I guess that's true. I'd go away.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7b6
STRING: [Torta] “Exactly. Regardless, I got here first.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7d6
STRING: [Chris] “What time did you get here?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x808
STRING: [Torta] “Almost exactly nine o'clock. I warmed up my
voice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x81e
STRING: [Chris] “Whoa...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x850
STRING: [Torta] “It takes a voice longer to warm up than an
instrument. I always come around thirty minutes early.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x870
STRING: [Chris] “Impressive.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8a2
STRING: [Torta] “Now, how about you?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8b8
STRING: Torta was already prepared, and said this to hurry me
up.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8ce
STRING: [Chris] “I'm almost ready, too.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8e4
STRING: But I must've become used to this, as I got ready while I
talked.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8fa
STRING: I set up my portable Fortelle and opened the sheet
music.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x922
STRING: [Torta] “Okay, let's play it through for now.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x938
STRING: The moment Torta said that, I thought I heard a knock
at the door.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x94e
STRING: [Chris] “Hmm?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x978
STRING: I thought it was my imagination, but when I looked out
the small window to make sure, I saw Ms. Cordell
peeking inside.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x98e
STRING: [Chris] “Mi... Ms. Cordell.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9a4
STRING: She couldn't hear me like that, so I quickly opened the
door.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9c0
STRING: [Chris] “G-Good morning.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9f2
STRING: [Cordell] “Good morning. I know it's early, but I'm glad
you're here. I guess we have Tortinita to thank for this.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa12
STRING: [Chris] “You got it...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa44
STRING: [Torta] “Oh, Ms. Cordell, good morning. What brings
you here?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa6c
STRING: [Cordell] “Good morning. I thought I'd drop by and see
the faces of my students and how they're doing, now
that the holiday is over.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa8c
STRING: [Chris] “I get the face part... But my condition?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xaaa
STRING: [Cordell] “I thought I'd watch you perform once again.
What do you say?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xadc
STRING: [Torta] “Ah, of course.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xaf2
STRING: [Chris] “Um, if you wouldn't mind, we'd be delighted.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb24
STRING: [Cordell] “That's the spirit. Very well, 1:30 at the usual
classroom.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb58
STRING: [Chris] “Oh, right.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb76
STRING: [Cordell] “Alright, keep up your normal practice until
then.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb9a
STRING: Having said her piece, Ms. Cordell hurried away.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xba6
STRING: She probably left to check on her other students.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbd8
STRING: [Torta] “Okay, now we have to practice more seriously
than ever.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbee
STRING: Torta seemed to brace herself all the more, as she said
this with a grave face.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc5c
STRING: [Torta] “Okay, we should get going.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc72
STRING: [Chris] “Huh? Oh, it's that time already.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc88
STRING: We had finished our morning practice and were eating
lunch in the cafeteria when Torta said this while
glancing at the clock.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc9e
STRING: It was still a little too early, but that was just like Torta.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcb4
STRING: It wouldn't hurt to go early, so I stood up with my lunch
tray and walked to the entrance.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcca
STRING: Torta threw the remains of the sandwich she made in
the trash and followed me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xce0
STRING: [Chris] “It was the same last time, but I'm a little
nervous.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd12
STRING: [Torta] “If this makes you nervous, what are you going
to do at the recital? You're delicate for a boy.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd32
STRING: [Chris] “Just more delicate than you, Torta.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd50
STRING: [Torta] “What's that mean?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd66
STRING: [Chris] “That's what I'm talking about...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd98
STRING: [Torta] “I wouldn't be able to do this if I was as delicate
as you, Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdae
STRING: [Chris] “Do what?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xde0
STRING: [Torta] “Lots of things...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe04
STRING: Torta said this in a slightly uncharacteristic tone, and left
as I was putting my tray down.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe64
STRING: [Chris] “Excuse me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xeb6
STRING: [Cordell] “Hmm? Ah, Chris and Torta. You're a little
early.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xecc
STRING: When we opened the door, Ms. Cordell was standing
right there.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xee2
STRING: She appeared to have some sheet music in her hand,
and looked like she was just about to go outside.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xef8
STRING: [Chris] “Do you have plans?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf16
STRING: [Cordell] “Yeah, it will only take five minutes... Can you
wait here for a little while?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf36
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah, we don't mind. It's our fault for coming
ten minutes early.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf5e
STRING: [Cordell] “Thanks. Alright, I'll be right back.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf82
STRING: My supervisor was gone, but Ms. Cordell must have had
a lot of things to do.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf98
STRING: I watched her walk away with quick steps.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfc0
STRING: [Torta] “Well, let's get everything ready.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfe4
STRING: All Torta had to do was put her sheet music on the
stand, and I made some simple adjustments to the
Fortelle.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xffa
STRING: My body was already loose, so I wasn't planning on
really practicing for the five minutes.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1022
STRING: I played something to pass the time and thought I heard
Torta whisper something next to me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1040
STRING: [Torta] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1056
STRING: I realized right away that she wasn't saying anything to
me and when I listened...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x106c
STRING: It was part of the song we would be playing.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1080
STRING: [Torta] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1096
STRING: The singing voice from that day overlapped that voice.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10a2
STRING: [Chris] “Torta...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10c4
STRING: I whispered without thinking... I whispered her name.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10ec
STRING: [Torta] “Hmm? What? You stopped playing?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1102
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... No, I just kind of...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1134
STRING: [Torta] “So, is something wrong?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x114a
STRING: [Chris] “Oh, it's nothing.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x117c
STRING: [Torta] “You're weird...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11a0
STRING: Torta returned her gaze to the sheet music and started
singing softly again, like she was checking the notes.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11b6
STRING: Their voices were similar... But I suppose that was to be
expected.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11f8
STRING: [Cordell] “Sorry to keep you waiting. It seems that
you're both ready, so would you like to start?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1218
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... Yeah.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1236
STRING: [Cordell] “Very well, begin.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1268
STRING: [Torta] “Y-Yes.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x130c
STRING: [Cordell] “That was quite good.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1322
STRING: Ms. Cordell smiled in spite of herself, as if in admiration.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x132e
STRING: [Chris] “Thank you very much.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1360
STRING: [Torta] “＊sigh＊ Thank you.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1376
STRING: Torta looked satisfied as she let out a big breath.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x139e
STRING: [Cordell] “That being said...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13c8
STRING: [Chris] “Huh? Were there any problems?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13e6
STRING: [Cordell] “No, none in particular.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1410
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊ That's good, then.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x142e
STRING: [Cordell] “Keep working just like that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1444
STRING: [Chris] “Yes, ma'am.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1462
STRING: [Torta] “Yes, ma'am.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14a2
STRING: [Cordell] “Hmm...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14b8
STRING: Ms. Cordell said this in a grudging tone.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14c4
STRING: Even I knew that we didn't do a very good job.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14d0
STRING: [Chris] “Sorry...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14ee
STRING: [Cordell] “The music itself wasn't bad.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1504
STRING: [Chris] “R-Really...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1522
STRING: [Cordell] “That's not a compliment... That's just your
nature.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1538
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... Oh.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1556
STRING: [Cordell] “As for you, Chris, you just have an excellent
tone.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x156c
STRING: [Chris] “Is that not a compliment?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x159e
STRING: [Torta] “If it was about vocals, I think you'd say, ‘It's a
nice voice, but...’”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15c6
STRING: [Torta] “There are plenty of amateurs with nice voices,
it's not a compliment.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15ee
STRING: [Cordell] “Exactly. The lack of serious practice is to
blame. It's not good you don't realize that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x160e
STRING: [Chris] “Sorry...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x162c
STRING: [Cordell] “No matter. You just need more practice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1656
STRING: [Chris] “Yes, ma'am.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1670
STRING: Our performance over, we were cleaning up to go back
to the practice room, and Ms. Cordell called out from
behind us.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x169c
STRING: [Cordell] “Oh, I have something I want to talk to you
about before I leave. Could you stay behind?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16d0
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... Yes.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x16ee
STRING: [Cordell] “Not you, Chris. I was talking to Tortinita.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x172a
STRING: [Torta] “Oh... Yeah, that's okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1740
STRING: They were behind me so I didn't see, but it seemed that
Ms. Cordell was looking at Torta when she said that.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x175e
STRING: [Cordell] “It has to do with vocals. You may leave, Chris.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x177e
STRING: [Chris] “Oh, if that's the case, I'll go.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17b0
STRING: [Torta] “Okay, you go back first. Use the same practice
room if it's open. If it's not... Umm, will we be finished
soon?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17e2
STRING: [Cordell] “In four or five minutes.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1800
STRING: [Torta] “Alright. Can you go back to the practice room,
Chris? I don't want them to fill up.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1820
STRING: [Chris] “Got it. Uh, then I'll be going.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x183e
STRING: [Cordell] “Yeah. I'm generally here all day, so come by if
you want to ask me something or you want me to
watch you practice. I'll do whatever I can.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1868
STRING: [Chris] “Thank you very much.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x189a
STRING: [Torta] “Alright, I'll just be a minute.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18b0
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18c6
STRING: Saying only this, I walked out.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x18fe
STRING: Luckily the practice room we were using was available.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x190a
STRING: I just killed time until Torta was finished and came back.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1916
STRING: I thought again about Ms. Cordell coming while we
were practicing, and how we'd had to stop.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x192c
STRING: About that and how Arie and Torta's singing was
similar.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1938
STRING: That may have been obvious.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1944
STRING: But even if they did have the same voice, I didn't think
I'd mistake one for the other.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x195a
STRING: It was difficult to explain with words,; it was their
characters, their behavior...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1970
STRING: I could definitely tell the difference between even the
slight variations in their tones.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1986
STRING: However... I should probably say that I thought I did.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x199c
STRING: I understood now Torta's remark that they each
covered for what the other lacked.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19f2
STRING: [Torta] “Sorry to keep you waiting.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a1c
STRING: Torta returned after about thirty minutes had passed.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a32
STRING: [Chris] “Oh, welcome back...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a64
STRING: [Torta] “Okay, we don't have time to fool around. Let's
practice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a84
STRING: [Chris] “That took a pretty long time, didn't it?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1ab6
STRING: [Torta] “Yeah. It was kind of a complicated talk.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1acc
STRING: [Chris] “Even so, you look fairly pleased.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1afe
STRING: [Torta] “A little... Anyway, practice, practice!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b14
STRING: Torta said this laughingly to kick me out of the funk I
was about to sink into.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b2a
STRING: I was fine with that, and we were tired regardless.
